Package: libgtk2-ex-celllayout-base-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.8), libgtk2-perl (>= 1:1.180), libglib-ex-objectbits-perl, ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Basic Gtk2::CellLayout interface implementation
 Gtk2::Ex::Celllayout::Base provides a basic set of functions for use
 by new data viewer widgets written in Perl wanting to implement the
 Gtk2::CellLayout interface.
